description: A crew in London breaks down a 70-foot dinosaur replica.
maintext: A crew of six people spent three weeks dismantling a 70-foot dinosaur replica in Natural History Museum in London.The life sized diplodocus replica, known as Dippy, was shown being taken apart in a time-lapse video. The dinosaur is scheduled to go on tour across the U.K.
title: Crew breaks down a 70-foot dinosaur replica
